{"id": 148, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何烘焙让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。生活研究所每周都会推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。\r\n", "record_count": 1423, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194634nk7MctzBZfsD2OdX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-11-17T08:40:57Z", "questions": [{"id": 126, "title": "如何烘焙让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何烘焙让你更像一个中产阶级？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1070, "content": "一个下厨房的作者，而非读者", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719371134vBfgpZNdnziOb2.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1071, "content": "烘焙用具不一定都用到，但必须准备齐全", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193821Uqzr0DMHst5Q3xy4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1072, "content": "不能用随便的小烤箱，必须用嵌入式的", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925486ogWTfdH98yAPqDw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1073, "content": "自己养酵母", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194001od9UaBCRsJhFWVMp.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1074, "content": "绝不买半成品", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192549VMBUO2FYvPLokjA5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1075, "content": "餐具必须要美", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193821kiI5GCsULgXejWqA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1076, "content": "不必自己洗碗", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925498wHsINK1GrE9J7XA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}